-- Germany confident on successful U.S. deficit talks
-- 
-- Fri Jul 15, 2011 4:52pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/15/us-budget-germany-idUSTRE76E1JF20110715

 

 BERLIN  (Reuters) - Germany is confident that agreement will be reached in budget deficit talks in the United States, government spokesman Steffen Seibert said on Friday. 

 "The German government is watching very closely what is being discussed," he said at a regular news briefing. "We are confident that ultimately there will be a compromise, we hope it will be soon." (Reporting by  David Milliken ,  Brian Rohan )